## Model Routing - MANDATORY
# See docs/model-routing.md for full explanation
# REQUIRES: llm CLI (pip install llm) and a Gemini API key in api-keys.json
#
# RULE: Before spending Sonnet credits, check if this task belongs to a cheaper model.

| Task | Model | Command |
|------|-------|---------|
| Summarize a file | Gemini 2.5 Flash | llm -m gemini-2.5-flash "summarize" < file.txt |
| Explain a code snippet | Gemini 2.5 Flash | pipe snippet |
| Generate a regex or query | Gemini 2.5 Flash | prompt directly |
| Write tests for trivial code | Gemini 2.5 Flash | pipe the file |
| Codebase Q&A | graphify query | never raw Sonnet file reads |
| Multi-file code changes | Claude Sonnet | current session - justified |
| Complex debugging | Claude Sonnet | only after graphify query fails |
| Architecture decisions | Claude Sonnet | |
| Novel unsolved problems | Claude Opus | only if Sonnet fails twice |

