## Vault Conventions
# INSTRUCTIONS: These rules keep your vault as a connected knowledge graph.
# Every file must link to at least one other file. No orphans.

Every new vault file MUST include:
1. H1 title on line 1
2. Parent: [[Folder/ParentFile]] on line 2
3. At least one wikilink to a related file using [[Path/FileName]] syntax
4. After creating a new file, update the parent to link back to it

File naming: Title Case. Match folder structure (Projects/Active/MyProject.md).

Vault logging - mandatory after every meaningful task:
- New feature built -> update Projects/Active/[ProjectName].md
- Decision made -> append to Decisions Log/Decisions Log.md
- Knowledge learned -> write to Knowledge Base/[Topic]/[Topic].md
- Session ends -> update Session Takeaways/Session Takeaways.md

